imdb.plot outline: Mayo Clinic and Gaiam share a new, integrated approach to managing and reducing high blood pressure. Mayo Clinic doctors share what you need to know about high blood pressure, integrative therapies, diet strategies to help lower blood pressure, gentle yoga to improve circulation and release tension, stress-relieving guided meditation, and easy practical lifestyle tips. Changing the way you live can change the way you feel with high blood pressure.
